866
00:43:59,500 --> 00:44:00,950
Nadie sabe nada.

867
00:44:00,968 --> 00:44:02,695
Estamos libres de sospecha.

868
00:44:02,770 --> 00:44:04,197
Vamos a matar a este tipo...

869
00:44:04,200 --> 00:44:06,238
