941
00:47:21,951 --> 00:47:24,215
No, no. Todo está bien.

942
00:47:24,286 --> 00:47:26,310
Dale un beso de mi parte.

943
00:47:26,387 --> 00:47:28,082
Llegaré pronto a casa.

944
00:47:28,156 --> 00:47:29,720
Bien. Gracias.

945
00:47:31,459 --> 00:47:32,485
Dilo otra vez.

946
00:47:32,660 --> 00:47:33,592
Esposa.

947
00:47:33,661 --> 00:47:35,325
