1401
01:11:41,043 --> 01:11:42,977
...con tus huellas en la jeringa.

1402
01:11:44,045 --> 01:11:45,043
Jack.

1403
01:11:45,914 --> 01:11:47,308
Vamos, Jack.

1404
01:11:48,182 --> 01:11:49,300
Déjame entrar.

1405
01:11:50,251 --> 01:11:51,141
Jack.

1406
01:11:51,819 --> 01:11:53,110
Vamos.

1407
01:11:53,888 --> 01:11:54,952
Por favor.

1408
01:11:56,224 --> 01:11:58,318
Maldito seas.
Abre la maldita puerta.

1409
01:11:58,492 --> 01:12:00,123
¡Abre la puerta ahora!

1410
01:12:00,594 --> 01:12:01,921
¡Jack, por favor!

1411
01:12:02,596 --> 01:12:03,763
¡Abre la maldita puerta!

1412
01:12:03,800 --> 01:12:04,854
Adiós, Sam.

