1425
01:12:43,166 --> 01:12:44,825
Una ampolleta de epinefrina.

1426
01:12:45,401 --> 01:12:46,529
<i>Clay.</i>

1427
01:12:46,602 --> 01:12:48,092
Vamos, Clayton.

1428
01:12:48,171 --> 01:12:50,462
