1440
01:13:16,629 --> 01:13:17,553
200.

1441
01:13:17,731 --> 01:13:18,689
Listo.

1442
01:13:20,200 --> 01:13:21,132
Vamos.

1443
01:13:21,201 --> 01:13:22,660
Tengo que mostrarte algo.

1444
01:13:23,903 --> 01:13:25,393
No quiero ver esto.

1445
01:13:25,472 --> 01:13:27,029
Temo que tienes que hacerlo.

1446
01:13:28,406 --> 01:13:29,800
