1451
01:13:41,080 --> 01:13:42,519
<i>...vamos a hablar de esto?</i>

1452
01:13:42,587 --> 01:13:43,918
<i>¿Cuántas malditas veces?</i>

1453
01:13:43,988 --> 01:13:45,553
